-- Alon Big Spring Refinery in Texas Has Sulfur Recovery Unit Trip
-- B y   M a r k   C h e d i a k
-- 2012-09-30T14:30:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-30/alon-big-spring-refinery-in-texas-has-sulfur-recovery-unit-trip.html
Alon USA Energy Inc. reported
emissions after a sulfur recovery unit and gas compressor trip
due to a power failure yesterday at the Texas refinery caused by
heavy rain, a filing with state regulators showed.  The event began at 1 a.m. and ended at 2:33 a.m. local
time, according to the filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mark Chediak in  San Francisco  at 
 mchediak@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
